latestIgtvVideos.caption:
AD/Talking all things @beautypie over on IGTV today – and we have a code! 
Beauty pie is a membership club for beauty lovers, it gives you access to a huge collection of skincare products, make-up and hair care products from the world’s leading labs, but without paying for the middlemen, retailers costs or celebrity marketing, this in turn gets you quality products for amazing prices. 
Depending on which membership you choose, you get a monthly allowance to spend on products. We have a code, which will get you £50 of extra allowance in your first month onto your account when signing up, the code is LSSSENTME 
Sam will be sharing all her favourites and recommendations in the video above. G&S x
